  "original_title": "\u0d8b\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0da2\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A piece of crap from a support teacher",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that they were arrested in connection with an incident where a school teacher who runs tutoring classes allegedly took nude photos of four female students who attended the advanced level classes.",
        "Police also said that the suspected teacher runs tutoring classes in Rambodagalla and Mawathagama areas and the suspect is a school teacher.",
        "The students told the police that they took the four students in the car and stopped the car and took these photos while saying that they were going to teach them more.",
        "The police also said that when checking the suspect's cell phone, the nude photos of the four female students were recorded on it."
      ],
